{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Notification.onclick","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/click_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notifications_API\">Notifications API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>コンストラクター</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/Notification\"><code>Notification()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/actions\"><code>actions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/badge\"><code>badge</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/body\"><code>body</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/data\"><code>data</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/dir\"><code>dir</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/icon\"><code>icon</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/image\"><code>image</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/lang\"><code>lang</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/maxActions\"><code>maxActions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/permission\"><code>permission</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/renotify\"><code>renotify</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/requireInteraction\"><code>requireInteraction</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/silent\"><code>silent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/tag\"><code>tag</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/timestamp\"><code>timestamp</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/title\"><code>title</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/vibrate\"><code>vibrate</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/requestPermission\"><code>requestPermission()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><em><code>click</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/error_event\"><code>error</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/show_event\"><code>show</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Web Notifications に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/NotificationEvent\"><code>NotificationEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/getNotifications\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration.getNotifications()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/ServiceWorkerRegistration/showNotification\"><code>ServiceWorkerRegistration.showNotification()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>注:</strong> この機能は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Worker</a> 内で利用可能です</p>\n</div><div class=\"notecard secure\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>安全なコンテキスト用:</strong> この機能は一部またはすべての<a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">対応しているブラウザー</a>において、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Security/Secure_Contexts\">安全なコンテキスト</a> (HTTPS) でのみ利用できます。</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p><strong><code>onclick</code></strong> は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a> インターフェイスのプロパティで、 <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element/click_event\" title=\"click\"><code>click</code></a> イベントを受信するイベントリスナーを指定します。これらのイベントはユーザーが表示されている <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a> をクリックしたときに発生します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"構文","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><var>Notification</var>.onclick = function(event) { ... };\n</pre>\n\n<p>既定の動作は、この通知に関連した<a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/browsers.html#browsing-context\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">閲覧コンテキスト</a>へフォーカスを移動することです。この動作をさせたくない場合は、イベントオブジェクトの <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault\" title=\"preventDefault()\"><code>preventDefault()</code></a> を呼び出してください。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>以下の例では、 <code>onclick</code> ハンドラーを使用して、通知がクリックされたときにウェブページを新しいタブで開くようにしています (<code>_blank</code> を含めて指定することで指定)。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>notification<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onclick</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  event<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventDefault</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// prevent the browser from focusing the Notification's tab</span>\n  window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'http://www.mozilla.org'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'_blank'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">備考</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://notifications.spec.whatwg.org/#dom-notification-onclick\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Notifications API<br><small lang=\"ja\">onclick の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n   <td>Living standard</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.Notification.onclick","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/click_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification\"><code>Notification</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notifications_API/Using_the_Notifications_API\">通知 API の使用</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"構文","id":"syntax"},{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"onclick は Notification インターフェイスのプロパティで、 click イベントを受信するイベントリスナーを指定します。これらのイベントはユーザーが表示されている Notification をクリックしたときに発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Notification: click event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Notification.onclick","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Notification.onclick","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Notification.onclick","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/notification/click_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/notification/click_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification","title":"Notification"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/Notification/click_event","title":"Notification.onclick"}],"pageTitle":"Notification.onclick - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}